  "title": "Personal Assistant [ No Exp|Fresh Grads Welcomed! ]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours: </strong><br />⏰ Mon to Fri | 9.30am to 6pm<br /><br /><strong>Location: </strong><br />📍 Somerset [Near MRT]<br /><br /><strong>Job Description: </strong><br />We are looking for a proactive and organized <strong>Personal Assistant</strong> to support our Wealth Director. This role is perfect for someone who wants hands-on experience, exposure to wealth advisory operations, and the chance to grow in a dynamic environment.<br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong>: <br />📌 Assist Wealth Director with daily office and administrative tasks to keep everything running smoothly.<br />📌 Prepare and organize documents, reports, presentations, and client materials.<br />📌 Handle emails, phone calls, correspondence, and other communications.<br />📌 Keep office supplies stocked and coordinate with vendors and service providers.<br />📌 Assist in planning and coordinating company or client events, meetings, and conferences.<br />📌 Arrange travel, accommodation, and itineraries as needed.<br />📌 Support the management team with special projects and ad-hoc tasks.<br />📌 Assist with general office tasks such as expense claims and other support duties.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements: </strong><br />✔️ Good organisational, communication, and time management skills.<br />✔️ Customer service experience is a <strong>big plus</strong>, even if you have minimal office experience.<br />✔️ Comfortable working independently and juggling multiple tasks.<br /><br /><strong>Think you’d be a great fit? </strong><br />Come join our team and grow your skills while supporting a Wealth Director. We look forward to meeting you!<br />📱 WhatsApp us at <strong>8963 7656</strong><br />📧 Email your resume to <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><strong>enquiries.arch@gmail.com</strong></p>",
